metadata.name: MVID-Pass
metadata.description: METAVERSE IDEA (MVID) is the first NFT collab with many toy designers, collections, and projects. The unique and high-quality generated 3D NFT collection on the Ethereum Blockchain. The MVID grant holders have access to exclusive drops/downloads in many different 3D formats as your 3D avatar for other metaverse platforms, future projects, and the community. Also, have a chance to win up to 3 Top-Notch Designer Toys Collection per week; HOLD more means it is possibly winning more than one prize in the same week.
